{"id":1239,"date":"2024-08-04T00:23:25","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T00:23:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1239"},"modified":"2024-08-04T00:23:25","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T00:23:25","slug":"mission-041","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-041\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #041: Neighbourly Assistance"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #041: Neighbourly Assistance<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Frozen Heights, southeast house &#8211; old man inside<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Accepted Mission #001 from Professor Log<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Bring an Antidote from the Bellin Town Mart to the old man in Frozen Heights<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: Psychic Gem or Rock Gem or Ground Gem<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Your neighbour in Frozen Heights has a simple task for you &#8211; go and buy an Antidote for him at the Poke Mart in Bellin Town. If you bring it to him, he\u2019ll give you a typed Gem matching your starter Pok\u00e9mon.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/041\/01-pokemon-unbound-your-neighbours-house.jpg\" alt=\"Your neighbours\u2019 house \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Your neighbours\u2019 house<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head to the southeast part of Frozen Heights and visit the house here with an old married couple.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/041\/02-pokemon-unbound-a-quest-from-your-neighbour.jpg\" alt=\"A quest from your neighbour \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>A quest from your neighbour<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The old man needs an Antidote from a Poke Mart, and considering there\u2019s one in nearby Bellin Town, it should be easy for you to pick it up.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/041\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-poke-mart.jpg\" alt=\"The Poke Mart \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Poke Mart<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Poke Mart is in the southeast corner of Bellin Town, and an Antidote costs P100.<\/p>\n<p>Head back to Frozen Heights to finish your delivery.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/041\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-old-man-gives-us-a-gem.jpg\" alt=\"The old man gives us a Gem \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The old man gives us a Gem<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When we hand over the Antidote, the old man gives us a Gem that can power up a single move. The type of the Gem depends on your starter Pok\u00e9mon.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey center\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Gem<\/th>\n<th>Starter<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Psychic Gem<\/td>\n<td>Beldum<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Rock Gem<\/td>\n<td>Pupitar<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ground Gem<\/td>\n<td>Gible<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1240,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1239","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1239","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1240"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1239"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1239"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}